<h1><%= @product.name.capitalize %></h1>
<h3>Calories per Serving: <%= @product.calories %></h3>

Stores found:
<ul>
	<% @product.stores.each do |store| %>
		<li>
			<%= link_to store.name, store_path(store) %>
			<%= store.address %>
		</li>
	<% end %>
</ul>

Lists belongs to:
<ul>
	<% @product.lists.each do |list| %>
		<li><%= link_to list.name, list_path(list) %></li>
	<% end %>
</ul>

Add to a Store:
<%= render 'add_store' %>